<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hạyjy ạlạkẖtṭạf</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hạ yjy ạlạ̹kẖtṭạf whạ nkẖṭf ʿ ạlsḥạb
 nnsy̱ ạlạ̉lạ̉m ʿly̱ ạldwạm(wnsẖwf kl ạlạ̉ḥbạb)2
 ạlqrạr- qrb yjy yswʿ rby (hạnsy̱ hmy lmạ ạ̉rạh)2
 2- hdẖạ hw rjạy yswʿ rby jạy
 swf ạ̉rạh ạ̉rạh bạljrwḥ (rby ḥbyb ạlrwḥ)2
 3- ywm ạllqạ qryb fyh ạ̉ry̱ ạlḥbyb
 yạ̉kẖdẖnạ ʿndh bṣwt ạltrḥạb (hnạk fy byt ạlạ̉b)2
 4- ạ̉shrwạ yạ mw̉mnyn kwnwạ fy ạlạ̹ntẓạr
 dạ yswʿ wʿdnạ wwʿdh ạ̉myn (yạ̉ty yạkẖdẖ ạlạ̉brạr)2</lyrics>
